<p>&#160;</p>
<h3>Colloqium for Information Systems Security Education (CISSE)</h3>
<p><a href="https://cisse.info/about/award-recipients">Founder's Award</a></p>
<p>This award honors an individual from business, academia or government who has made a significant contribution toward furthering the state of information systems security education.</p>
