<h3>Computing Research Association (CRA)</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.cra.org/">Computing Research Association (CRA) website</a></p>
<p><strong> <a href="https://www.cra.org/Activities/awards/service/home.html">Distinguished Service Award</a> </strong></p>
<p>CRA makes this award, usually annually, to someone who has made an outstanding service contribution to the computing research community. This award recognizes service in the areas of government affairs, professional societies, publications or conferences, and leadership that has a major impact on computing research.</p>
