<p><strong> <a href="https://www.computer.org/volunteering/awards/booth">Taylor Booth Award</a>&#160; </strong></p>
<p>Awarded for an outstanding record in computer science and engineering education. The individual must meet two or more of the following criteria in the computer science and engineering field: achieving recognition as a teacher of renown; writing an influential text; leading, inspiring, or providing significant educational content during the creation of a curriculum in the field; inspiring others to a career in computer science and engineering education.</p>
